scenes.description: Mori Calliope presents her birthday merchandise, including a water bottle, a situational voice pack, and a complete set purchase bonus featuring an autographed postcard and a hololive OFFICIAL CARD GAME PR card.
MC section where Mori Calliope hypes up the audience for the upcoming performances.
Mori Calliope performs the song "Ouroboros" on stage with backup dancers.
